# AVPlayerInterstitialEvent.TimelineOccupancy.singlePoint

**Case**

The event occupies a single point on the integrated timeline.

## Declaration

```swift
case singlePoint
```

## Values

- **AVPlayerInterstitialEvent.TimelineOccupancy.fill**: The event fills the integrated timeline with the duration of this event.
